{"tid":2102531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多名議辦作票站區議員收房委會警告信   區議員：證明政府非常害怕","createTime":"2020-07-10T13:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T19:26:11.000Z","uid":56115,"like":216,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"33f3c30999383e68568268c6ecce5176ca04e8e3","tid":2102531,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"民主派初選將於明天（11 日）及後天（12 日）舉行，不少票站是區議員辦事處和「黃店」。惟在投票日前，有多名民主派議員收到房委會警告，指以議辦作為票站與區議會事務無關，或違反租約條約，房委會將按實際情況採取適當跟進行動；「黃店」Sogno Gelato亦在前日（8 日）收到業主信和置業通知，指把店舖用作初選票站或會因違約封鋪，店主最終取消票站。其中一名收到房委會警告信的區議員、民主黨的賴文輝指，房署的說法非常荒謬，但他不擔心，「政府越打壓，證明政府非常害怕非建制派集中票源」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8-%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E8%AD%B0%E8%BE%A6%E4%BD%9C%E7%A5%A8%E7%AB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E6%94%B6%E6%88%BF%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E4%BF%A1-%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97%E8%A2%AB%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E9%81%95%E7%B4%84%E5%B0%81%E8%88%96-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E5%AE%B3%E6%80%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2588%259D%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E4%25BF%25A1-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25BA%2597%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E9%2581%2595%25E7%25B4%2584%25E5%25B0%2581%25E8%2588%2596-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E6%2580%2595%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=d1ff11ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fp